                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "As a swift action, a trophy hunter can designate a creature they can see within 60 feet as their prey. This designation remains for a number of hours equal to the trophy hunter\u2019s CR, until the marked prey dies, or until the trophy hunter designates another creature as their prey. A trophy hunter gains a bonus equal to half their CR to Survival checks to track their prey and to weapon damage rolls against their prey.",
